reviewText: You have to love everything kristofferson to really like this DVD. If you don't it's just ok.

Just couldn't wait for it to arrive! AND it did, promptly. It was more than I expected. Well packaged and to top it all, there was MY HERO, KRIS KRISTOFFERSON chatting away as though he was sitting in my own home! Thank you for your quick and attentive service. ANN WESKIN. PS: Worth every penny!
